This page is about library <tt>[[modeline-win.el]]</tt>, which highlights the [[buffer]] name in the [[mode-line]] for the selected [[window]].  You need Emacs 24.4 or later to use this library.

[[minor mode|Minor mode]] `mlw-mode-line-buf-id-sel-win-mode' turns on this highlighting.

You can [[Customize|customize]] [[face]] `mlw-mode-line-buffer-id-selected-window' for the highlighting.





----

